            <title>[OAK-714] Potential unsynchronised concurrent access to name space map in LocalNameMapper</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-714</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The name space map is referenced by &lt;tt&gt;SessionImpl&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;LocalNameMapper&lt;/tt&gt;. A comment at the former reference states &quot;This map is only accessed from synchronized methods&quot; which is not true for the latter reference. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
